skie dziecko. Ale jak tu się nie wyróżniać, mając nadprzyrodzone moce? Juan López ma rentgen w oczach, czyta w myślach, umie latać i jest w stanie zatrzymać pędzący wagon metra. Jak po tym wszystkim wrócić do pracy i być normalnym facetem? A może Superlópez nie potrzebuje do szczęścia niczego poza porannym croissantem?","popularity":1.8675,"poster_path":"/7doCBDNnEITiRg4LPI7wK1jdb4p.jpg","release_date":"2018-11-23","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":5.594,"vote_count":282,"credit_id":"591b11f1925141585206df24","department":"Directing","job":"Director"},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/ot4vGoUlmr27hSOPk0VhYKDZ8dD.jpg","genre_ids":[10751,18,10402],"id":1306284,"title":"Wolfgang","original_language":"ca","original_title":"Wolfgang (Extraordinari)","overview":"Dziewięcioletni Wolfgang po nagłej śmierci matki zostaje zmuszony zamieszkać z ojcem Carlesem, którego nigdy nie poznał.","popularity":1.0955,"poster_path":"/cZhZ574UhzztxFzRi7aljhooUZ1.jpg","release_date":"2025-03-14","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":6.558,"vote_count":52,"credit_id":"6671e354c9fe650c9d6aba6d","department":"Directing","job":"Director"},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/nQArfBFVCLd7lPt2CJxS5uLwhR.jpg","genre_ids":[35,12],"id":1139174,"title":"Treitum","original_language":"en","original_title":"Treitum","overview":"","popularity":0.7439,"poster_path":"/4JVTO0uGSoBkOwwLvYZKo0dSZY1.jpg","release_date":"2001-01-01","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":7.0,"vote_count":1,"credit_id":"6486a8a7028f14013b867b45","department":"Directing","job":"Director"},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/nQArfBFVCLd7lPt2CJxS5uLwhR.jpg","genre_ids":[35,12],"id":1139174,"title":"Treitum","original_language":"en","original_title":"Treitum","overview":"","popularity":0.7439,"poster_path":"/4JVTO0uGSoBkOwwLvYZKo0dSZY1.jpg","release_date":"2001-01-01","softcore":false,"video":false,"vote_average":7.0,"vote_count":1,"credit_id":"6486a8bbe2726001287aa9b6","department":"Writing","job":"Writer"},{"adu